The invention discloses a method for switching a main power supply and a backup power supply and a switching circuit. The switching circuit comprises a main power supply switch, a backup power supply switch, a first switch control logic to a fourth switch control logic, a main power supply detection circuit and a switch control signal generation circuit, wherein, the main power supply switch comprises a first PMOS pipe and a second PMOS pipe; the first PMOS pipe and the second PMOS pipe are connected in series between the main power supply and an output node; the backup power supply switch comprises a third PMOS pipe and a fourth PMOS pipe; the third PMOS pipe and the fourth PMOS pipe are connected in series between the output node and the backup power supply; and the switch control signal generation circuit determines connection and stop of the first PMOS pipe to the fourth PMOS pipe according to input of the main power supply detection circuit. Independent substrates of the PMOS pipes are generated through a mode of cross coupling, which not only can avoid substrate creepage, but also can meet the requirement of respectively connecting and stopping two serially connected PMOS pipes.
