The invention discloses a power consumption controlling method and a controlling system of a Flash memory, the invention includes the following steps: 1) a read instruction signal which is synchronous to the clock is sent through a Flashing controller: 2) the read instruction signal is transformed into a chip enabling signal which ensures that the impulse width of the chip enabling signal is smaller than the clock period but not smaller than the shortest visiting time of the Flash memory: 3) the chip enabling signal unseals the Flash controller and reads the data of the Flash memory. The impulse width of the chip enabling signal which controls the switch of the Flash memory is smaller than the period of the Flash controller, which ensures that the reading operation of the Flash memory keeps a low consumption no matter the clock is fast or slow, thus the consumption of the whole Flash memory is lowered.

